							br
							| Learning and Organizational Change.
							br
							| President of EPIC.
					.col-md-4
						img.img-responsive.margin-center(src='images/AlexPopelard.jpg', alt='Alexandre Popelard')
						h5.text-bold ALEXANDRE POPELARD
						br
						h5 Kellogg School of Management
							br
							| MMM(MBA+MEM)
							br
							| Senior Engineer at Toyota.
					.col-md-4
						img.img-responsive.margin-center(src='images/SuzeeHan.jpg', alt='Suzee Han')
						h5.text-bold SUZEE HAN
						br
						h5 Northwestern Junior
							br
							| Biological Science
							br
							| Director of Project Pitch			
